      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 146,
      "message": "Its not clear what in spec will determine these properties to be setup by DCAE platform? These appear more suitable as application config and can be driven through blueprint as common parameter rather than being defined per stream.\nWe could standardize all DMAAP (mr/dr/kafka) connection to be authenticated using aaf username/pwd.",
